Who will have access to your personal health information according to the confidentiality statement in the new consent form?
A) Only the principal investigator and the research team; 
B) The principal investigator, research team, and representatives from the sponsor, ethics committee, and relevant regulatory authority inspectors; 
C) Only the ethics committee and relevant regulatory authority inspectors; 
D) No one will have access to your personal health information.

Correct answer: B
